name: Track Master
description:
The End is as Nigh as you believe it to be!

Created in 72 hours for Winter Jam by SoloDevelopment

Generic rock assets and floor textures sourced from Kenney.nl. You're a legend, dude.

Character base mesh originally created by Meng Low, purchased at  https://www.artstation.com/marketplace/p/GblP/base-meshes-character-starter-kit-...

Animations generated using Mixamo.

Fonts sourced from DaFont (Public Pixel) and https://textcraft.net

All other assets and code made by myself. Enjoy!
